## ğŸ“Œ Overview

This project is a **Crop Production Dashboard** built to analyze and visualize agricultural data such as crop yield, rainfall, fertilizer usage, and production trends across different states. The dashboard helps stakeholders, policymakers, and farmers to make data-driven decisions for better crop management and resource allocation.

It integrates multiple datasets including crops, states, rainfall, and fertilizers to provide a **comprehensive view of agricultural performance**.

